The paper discusses the evaluation of explainable AI systems in the context of human-AI teams, which suggests a focus on human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The study also touches on issues related to cybersecurity (cs.CYBER) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the in-person think-aloud study suggests a focus on human-computer interaction (cs.HCI).
